Name: range
Description/Notes: Distance from the instrument's transducer head(s)

Name: c_sound
Description/Notes: Speed of sound used in velocity calculations

Name: angrt
Description/Notes: Angular rotation rate of the instrument

Name: corr
Description/Notes: Correlation between the sent and received pings.

Name: tke_vec
Description/Notes: Variance of velocity components (0: u'u', 1: v'v', 2: w'w')

Name: stress_vec
Description/Notes: Reynolds stress array (0: u'v', 1: u'w', 2: v'w')

Name: U_std
Description/Notes: Standard deviation of horizontal velocity magnitude

Name: psd
Description/Notes: Spectra, calculated as power spectral densities
